<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Due to its current limited nature, the existing filterset does not allow developers to create regex based filters that fulfill the on-the-fly creation of filters that implement the Filter Interface... to satisfy that, i propose Zend_Filter_Regex</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
